卓尔百货交通路店、和平街菜市场的市民朋友主动报备，同时要坚持不出户，保持一米线，也一定要戴好口罩，保护好自己。」 四川内江发现奥密克戎变异株存在两个位点变异，未在国省基因测序数据库中发现 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-fbe5207b01bec5c005491510a1abf5af_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/553114320"}}, "attached_info": "ClQIwd7zi+nxmaUsEAMaCDg1MTk3ODc1IO2s+5gGMAE4REAPcgk1NTMxMTQzMjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAPIBEwgBEg9kb21haW5fb3BlcmF0b3I="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "16_1662970294.8556254", "card_id": "Q_552680419", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 83}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价周深的新歌《花开忘忧》？听了歌，你想起谁了吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "你是否曾想过， 每当说一声再见，就会开启一个新的世界。 有一个平行时空，让所有遗憾变得圆满"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-84e61e0f4953975ae1830036780cb345_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "76 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/552680419"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iwd7zi+nxmaUsEAMaCDg1MTAxMTQyIIbd7ZgGMAQ4bEAQcgk1NTI2ODA0MTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "17_1662970294.8565412", "card_id": "Q_506470415", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 213}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你身边的癌症患者都是怎么发现自己得癌的？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "前同事忽然走了，原因是得了肺癌，从知道到走掉真的好快，夏天还会一起吃吃饭，很大个子一个人说没就没了，到现在还有点不敢相信是真的"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-bdaee5201b035629119e4abdf6aa8007_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/506470415"}}, "attached_info": "C